  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sports Teacher - Part time",
  "description": "<h2>Love kids? Love staying active? Join us as Program Leader at Gymkidz!</h2>\n<p>We run mobile gym sessions in preschools, and we’re looking for energetic team players to bring fun and movement to little ones aged 18 months to 6 years.</p>\n<h3><strong>Your Day at a Glance</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Head straight to the first preschool to meet your team (own transport).<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Help set up our colourful play and gym equipment.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Conduct fun, structured gym sessions together with your teammates.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Pack up and travel together (transport provided) to the next school after lunch.<br>\n</li>\n  <li>End your day by heading home directly from the final school location.<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Perks &amp; Schedule</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monday–Friday only<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Public holidays off<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Active, hands-on work — no sitting at a desk!<br>\n</li>\n  <li>No pre or post session prep/lesson planning required, all work to be done during session hours only<br>\n</li>\n  <li>All lesson plans and training provided on the job<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Opportunity to work with a fun-loving, supportive and energetic team<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You Need</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Able to speak good English<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Physically fit<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Love working with young children<br>\n</li>\n  <li>Cheerful, energetic, friendly, reliable, and willing to learn<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Perfect for those who love movement, teamwork, and meaningful work with kids!</h3>\n<h2><br></h2>",
